      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DYNAMIC ONE (1) wasn't beaten far at Rockingham last start when off a 59-day break in this company. Mahony remains in the saddle and she maps to get every chance again in the run. Nicely poised in this company and she can get the job done. MY DE GRECE (6) comes right back in trip today after tackling midweek company over 2200m most recently. She'll carry no weight for Jason Li and if she can remain close to her best off a freshen, she'll be in this for a long way. TOBIAN (8) looks close to a win, finishing in the placings at his last couple of runs including a third most recently over 1900m at Narrogin when beaten 2L. Whittington has registered two minor placings when on board. Should be involved in the finish. PUDDIN 'N' PIE (7) has missed the frame in both runs this time in, both on turf. Finished 12th at Pinjarra Scarpside fresh then again missed the frame at Albany over 1100m three-and-a-half weeks ago. Solid top-three prospects. WARBY RANGES (3) won't be far away.",
